{"tid":1465243,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[勸世]其實做錯事係難免，但最重要係要識得力挽狂瀾","createTime":"2019-08-13T15:55:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T12:05:00.000Z","uid":13754,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b735fe5608774a943e9d19070c2ccaa7ae7fdf4b","tid":1465243,"uid":13754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:55:10.000Z","msg":"幾錯嘅事做咗就做咗，下一步係要令件事唔會再惡化<br />\n<br />\n與其不斷指責，不如停一停，諗下可以點令件事收得好啲<br />\n<br />\n柒婆同班狗正正就係唔識呢樣嘢，我相信我哋一齊兄弟姊妹應該識㗎可？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://poster.keepcalmandposters.com/default/6011879_keep_calm_and_meditate_on.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fposter.keepcalmandposters.com%2Fdefault%2F6011879_keep_calm_and_meditate_on.jpg&h=d5e51f9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然好嬲好攰，但我哋必須保持頭腦清醒<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dnxzRS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dnxzRS</a>"},{"pid":"5135af5489c6ec349292ec362e230e903a652b7a","tid":1465243,"uid":13754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:57:40.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"7eb559872f79efe4e31ceef511469f8e0074e3a0","tid":1465243,"uid":13754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:59:17.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"ee3bb138709fbb1b801fe47a0da5b3b4c6caf3cb","tid":1465243,"uid":181088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:59:28.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"e02dba3995248e0f27c323192e84735dac9b643b","tid":1465243,"uid":13754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:00:25.000Z","msg":"五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可"},{"pid":"62da15f766df8a803ac8f308ea438af0bba782ee","tid":1465243,"uid":2002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:01:04.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"7a93259eed4893703c70844905992b191b77ae12","tid":1465243,"uid":13754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:01:34.000Z","msg":"不割𥱊<br />\n不篤灰<br />\n不指責"},{"pid":"06974fe3c6a7a72e6279531cfd1f542a31c92bd5","tid":1465243,"uid":13754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:02:34.000Z","msg":"Stand with HK"},{"pid":"6064650bf3ff4efdddd8de89b86290efce1c6ead","tid":1465243,"uid":13754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:07:16.000Z","msg":"人微言輕，有時去到現場都唔知可以點幫大家<br />\n<br />\n大家Get到就盡量推盡量同你身邊嘅人講，唔好再為今日件事互相指責，諗諗點再進步<br />\n<br />\n唔Gur嘅等完咗喺煲底可以唔戴面罩咁三口六面拆掂佢"},{"pid":"68bf69bec985959ce48f5753b0cd482d09a83536","tid":1465243,"uid":168492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:07:47.000Z","msg":"停止所有指責<br />\n理性討論<br />\n獨立思考<br />\n不割蓆"},{"pid":"3e6a732dbb476942d6d0d19dd222bb9bd584eac8","tid":1465243,"uid":13754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:07:58.000Z","msg":"日日咁多起伏個人真係好攰，大家好好休息<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f5d3d7b5ffd1ff30eb372d687e953bbea23e79c","tid":1465243,"uid":245033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:13:23.000Z","msg":"一邊諗緊點拆<br />\n例如大道歉行動<br />\n報紙+落街遍地開花文宣<br />\n同煲大用真槍前置事件<br />\n（有藍衫打人然後圍佢）<br />\n唔知呢D諗唔諗得過<br />\n<br />\n一邊抵銷緊消極情緒<br />\n突然前所未有咁焦慮<br />\n不過都冇比人拉嘅手足咁傷"},{"pid":"1b7dccd4ff9fdb58b951d13fe0f9ed2d39cb1b3a","tid":1465243,"uid":267044,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:15:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"88106d3c40222655e0c4d89dc863355034f7c36f","tid":1465243,"uid":263936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:15:39.000Z","msg":"但說好的 大家有咩事手拉手 咁住想衝動嘅人呢？"},{"pid":"d13cc15d0964d103a529a434aa93138a93e668c7","tid":1465243,"uid":13754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T00:56:05.000Z","msg":"我好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2716a7f45ec980b964f15b44165ebd7409c3031d","tid":1465243,"uid":289690,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:01:57.000Z","msg":"做翻一次中招撚<br />\n今鑊真係中曬招<br />\n隻記者擺放係棋<br />\n之前北角都講左<br />\n你打完你爽完啦<br />\n個運動俾你送中<br />\n<br />\n中招撚完<br />\n而家唸之後點做<br />\n1.冷處理、即時低調行時、避免群情洶湧既蝗蟲入境無差別襲擊港人<br />\n2.記者會交代所有已知事實並且去醫院看望受傷的人、包括手足<br />\n3.企硬、屌鳩埋黨媒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09f98082cbf2973dc48d5eba87b48f572b04a29e","tid":1465243,"uid":238736,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b735fe5608774a943e9d19070c2ccaa7ae7fdf4b","tid":1465243,"uid":13754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:55:10.000Z","msg":"幾錯嘅事做咗就做咗，下一步係要令件事唔會再惡化<br />\n<br />\n與其不斷指責，不如停一停，諗下可以點令件事收得好啲<br />\n<br />\n柒婆同班狗正正就係唔識呢樣嘢，我相信我哋一齊兄弟姊妹應該識㗎可？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://poster.keepcalmandposters.com/default/6011879_keep_calm_and_meditate_on.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fposter.keepcalmandposters.com%2Fdefault%2F6011879_keep_calm_and_meditate_on.jpg&h=d5e51f9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然好嬲好攰，但我哋必須保持頭腦清醒<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dnxzRS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dnxzRS</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:19:34.000Z","msg":"非常認同，政府係死不認錯同聆聽唔同意見，但我哋會<br />\n<br />\n我明白前線戰友既焦急，希望儘快迫使政府迴應<br />\n<br />\n但我哋要冷靜，唔能夠變成對手一樣，佢地卑鄙冷血殘忍甚至犯法，我哋唔要！<br />\n<br />\n大家都係戰友，戰術執行有唔好好正常，有錯就認，去修正<br />\n<br />\n就算多發一副文宣圖，同身邊朋友家人進行理性討論，讓佢地知道多少少真相，動搖佢地錯既觀念，都係做緊野！<br />\n<br />\n我哋係有良知有素質既香港人，有錯就認！但不割席，因為我哋都係愛香港，我哋愛大家，我哋係香港人！<br />\n<br />\n要清醒，冷靜！將每個人流既血同淚，化成文宣材料，不斷轉發！"},{"pid":"1cf8ecaf23e40900016eda355d66adb01db1c7c2","tid":1465243,"uid":13754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:21:28.000Z","msg":"不割𥱊<br />\n不指責<br />\n不分化"},{"pid":"418d6aab53ddec25214d2183d4559f0dadb0b14a","tid":1465243,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:21:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/irwo5By.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Firwo5By.jpg&h=f3c2efbd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e1f2acfcda9407dde4683802c8e001cf25c3f58b","tid":1465243,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:21:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/6c057950ed65cc1fac07eb212cfe3471/tumblr_nfv4w34Uby1qcbtvqo5_250.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F6c057950ed65cc1fac07eb212cfe3471%2Ftumblr_nfv4w34Uby1qcbtvqo5_250.gif&h=74060c35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[輸出革命］由今日起，不叫港獨，改叫「廣獨」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1447204\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1447204</a><br />\n<br />\n其實我地係唔需要洗佢地腦，甚至唔需要接觸任何人，要做既野只需要貼去多大陸人既地方都係廣獨／粵獨poster就得....<br />\n只要將廣獨思想文宣貼到通街都係，中共知道左就自然唔敢放自由行落黎<br />\n將廣獨思想輸出從而增加中共管治成本同時減少自由行黎香港！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7nZFbOE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7nZFbOE.png&h=4fd8318f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴打可以用下面條link去印，set左a5 size<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=1qG8N4AsnroP--EywjjvBhkhWvLzeCzeR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D1qG8N4AsnroP--EywjjvBhkhWvLzeCzeR&d=3XxoN59xZ6GKXDea4epuEy1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=6bd853d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=1qG8N4AsnroP--EywjjvBhkhWvLzeCzeR</a>"},{"pid":"7fc22ab36486235109245c898412b934df704699","tid":1465243,"uid":13754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:05:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://poster.keepcalmandposters.com/default/6011879_keep_calm_and_meditate_on.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fposter.keepcalmandposters.com%2Fdefault%2F6011879_keep_calm_and_meditate_on.jpg&h=d5e51f9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然好嬲好攰，但我哋必須保持頭腦清醒<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dnxzRS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dnxzRS</a>"}]}